Package game.template.elements

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Card
    This interface sets cards and makes them available on the cards box if it is possible, also choose cards if it is possible.
    Images
    This interface gets and sets images of elements
    Zombie
    This interface fixes everything which is related to zombies.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BucketHeadZombie
    This class sets bucket head zombie images and stores its state and properties.
    CherryBomb
    This class controls the time of showing card of cherry bomb and showing it.
    ConeHeadZombie
    This class sets cone head zombie images and stores its state and properties.
    FreezePeaShooter
    This class controls the time of showing card of freeze pea shooter, showing freeze pea shooter and shooting peas.
    LawnMower
    This class makes lawn maker and fixes its state and image, changes its x coordinate when lawn maker should move.
    Mushroom
    This class controls the time of showing card of mushroom and showing it.(only at night) Sets all images of mushroom.
    NormalZombie
    This class sets normal zombie images and stores its state and properties.
    Pea
    This class fixes the location of peas that peashooter and freeze pea shooter shoots, and controls the time of shooting peas.
    PeaShooter
    This class controls the time of showing card of pea shooter, showing pea shooter and shooting peas.
    Squash
    This class controls the time of showing card of squash and showing it.
    SunFlower
    This class controls the time of showing card of sunFlower and showing it.
    SunProducer
    This class is used for producing sun.
    WallNut
    This class controls the time of showing card of wall nut and showing it.
    Zombies
    This class controls zombies entrance and their movement, makes list of zombies which are in the game.
